messages.message: Is anyone using the UI for Test Runner? It's only being used via API, correct?
And are tests being managed with the app-server handlers?
i think so? cc @Varun Nandan to confirm since i know the sol eng team is currently using test runner to do UAT for Marketplace apps on AI Hub
The sol eng team didn't indicate in this thread (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/CKBRX13L5/p1740773306944049) they were using it, but maybe they are?

we get bug tickets (https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/EPD-3725) from them if test runner reports a decrease in accuracy or validation rate

it seems this doc (https://instabase.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/AE/pages/2139717650/AI+Hub+Applications+Regression+Test+Suite) indicates that this UAT process uses Test Runner
okay got it, I'll start by just taking out the legacy one then
